Third-party tools and services
------------------------------

This project uses external tools and services that are **not** distributed as
part of the extension package, but are involved in development, CI/CD, or
runtime environment. They remain under their own licenses:

- GitHub Actions:
  - `actions/checkout` — MIT License
  - `actions/setup-python` — MIT License
  - `softprops/action-gh-release` — MIT License
  - `kewisch/action-web-ext` — see its LICENSE (uses Mozilla `web-ext` under MPL 2.0)

- Platforms:
  - Mozilla Firefox and addons.mozilla.org (AMO) — MPL 2.0 and related licenses
  - Chromium-based browsers (Chrome, Edge, Opera) — BSD-style and vendor-specific licenses

These components are used as external services and infrastructure and are not
incorporated into the distributable source code of TS_switcher.
